00:03:41.888 --> 00:03:43.223  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
about the Emperor's scheme.

39
00:03:43.348 --> 00:03:46.434  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I know who you're referring to.

40
00:03:46.517 --> 00:03:48.478  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
