41
00:03:49.812 --> 00:03:52.106  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Tell us what he's
intending to do.

42
00:04:05.745 --> 00:04:09.540  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
