<i>at your hands.</i>

46
00:04:16.297 --> 00:04:17.507  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>Is that what you're saying?</i>

47
00:04:20.969 --> 00:04:23.638  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
