their inevitable annihilation.

50
00:04:28.601 --> 00:04:30.561  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>I see.</i>

51
00:04:30.645 --> 00:04:34.357  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
