to come with me.

55
00:04:43.324 --> 00:04:45.868  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>Don't forget.</i>
<i>I'm one of those humans</i>

56
00:04:45.952 --> 00:04:47.495  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>on the brink of destruction.</i>

57
00:04:47.662 --> 00:04:51.499  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
