for Humanity"?

61
00:05:01.050 --> 00:05:04.304  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
The Emperor has concluded
that implementing this plan

62
00:05:04.387 --> 00:05:07.015  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
