64
00:05:10.351 --> 00:05:11.769  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
We can't allow that.

65
00:05:11.853 --> 00:05:13.313  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
The 5% they're talking about

66
00:05:13.396 --> 00:05:15.606  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
