6 billion people will perish.

67
00:05:15.690 --> 00:05:16.858  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
It's genocide!

68
00:05:17.025 --> 00:05:20.111  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Even those that do survive
are still doomed.

69
00:05:20.194 --> 00:05:22.697  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
