to be victims of The Blessed.

70
00:05:22.780 --> 00:05:25.616  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Elevating emotions
over simple logic,

71
00:05:25.700 --> 00:05:27.869  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
