72
00:05:28.036 --> 00:05:31.122  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
It's a idea we can
ill afford to overlook.

73
00:05:31.289 --> 00:05:33.875  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Obviously. Precisely the reason

74
00:05:33.958 --> 00:05:35.585  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
we have been proceeding
in secret.

75
00:05:36.586 --> 00:05:40.840  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Then Ivan, he was telling us
we should thwart this intention?

76
00:05:47.180 --> 00:05:49.390  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
