79
00:05:54.228 --> 00:05:56.397  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
So you finally chose
to wake up, did you?

80
00:05:56.564 --> 00:05:58.483  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Yeah, thanks to all of you,

81
00:05:58.566 --> 00:06:00.902  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
but I seem to have
slept in too long.

82
00:06:01.069 --> 00:06:04.906  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
