snoozing sweetheart?

86
00:06:20.797 --> 00:06:22.507  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Catalina]
For the last few months,

87
00:06:22.590 --> 00:06:25.259  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Dynamic Ultra's
Aerospace R &amp; D department

88
00:06:25.343 --> 00:06:27.178  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
