of 400 kilometers.

93
00:06:38.689 --> 00:06:40.525  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasps] You don't mean...

94
00:06:40.691 --> 00:06:43.111  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Correct. The micro-drones
are all going to be released

95
00:06:43.194 --> 00:06:45.363  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-from that station.
-What?

96
00:06:45.446 --> 00:06:47.031  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasps]

