00:06:52.161 --> 00:06:54.455  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
you're not actually swallowing
this traitor's story?

100
00:06:54.622 --> 00:06:57.583  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
What proof does she have?
Why should we believe her?

101
00:06:57.750 --> 00:06:59.127  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Jet.

102
00:06:59.210 --> 00:07:01.170  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
