106
00:07:09.929 --> 00:07:11.556  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
undetermined element
has appeared.

107
00:07:11.722 --> 00:07:12.723  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasps]

108
00:07:13.724 --> 00:07:15.143  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
The Emperor is aware

109
00:07:15.226 --> 00:07:17.603  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
and apparently doesn't think
it's much of a problem,

110
00:07:17.687 --> 00:07:20.565  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
but that element has put
our plan at significant risk.

111
00:07:20.731 --> 00:07:24.110  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Even if that's true, how can you
betray them so easily?

112
00:07:25.111 --> 00:07:28.239  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Those people were your comrades
until only an hour ago.

113
00:07:28.322 --> 00:07:30.700  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
We have
no concept of friendship.

114
00:07:30.783 --> 00:07:32.326  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
We were only working together,

115
00:07:32.410 --> 00:07:34.620  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
because we had interests
that were shared.

116
00:07:34.787 --> 00:07:37.039  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
So once you part ways
with The Blessed,

117
00:07:37.123 --> 00:07:39.125  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
you have no feelings
for them whatsoever?

118
00:07:39.292 --> 00:07:40.960  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Why would I?

119
00:07:41.127 --> 00:07:42.670  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasps]

120
00:07:42.753 --> 00:07:44.839  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
